data.description: Here's the perfect home for you.  This fabulous, 2 story home, located in a wonderful family friendly neighborhood.  Features 2 story entry, wood flooring, office w/newer carpet, 3 great sized bedrooms & 2.5 baths.  Large family room features beautiful fireplace to create cozy nights.  Open concept kitchen & dining will be perfect for entertaining.  Partially finished basement offers extra space for recreation.  Beautiful backyard provides great space for making memories.  This house will go fast!
